  <div class="wa-section">
    <div class="wa-label">Prefer to send directly?</div>
    <p class="wa-sub">
      Send your portfolio and resume in any format — PDF, images, drive links, anything works.<br/>
      We're on WhatsApp and will get back to you.
    </p>
